HEADWORD: Securely
<hw>Se*cure"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a secure manner; without
fear or apprehension; without danger; safely.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His daring foe . . . <qex>securely</qex> him defied.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Securement</ent>⟦br⟧
